findings.title: I15: Code duplication
findings.description: Code duplication between LiquidityMining contract's `claim` function and LiquidityMiningInternal's `_calculateAccountRewards` function.

findings.title: H1: Inability to unstake when the contract runs out of rewards
findings.description: If the contract LiquidityMining run out of rewards, users will be unable to withdraw staked tokens.
